    v1 = 0.0

    v1 = 0.33
    tmp = ((wp.cos(tmp + 0.27) - (v2 + 0.97 / v2 + 0.06)) + v1)
    v0 = 0.62
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.cos(wp.exp(v0 + 0.94)))
